column16: With Torii Hunter batting, Shane Robinson picked off and caught stealing 2nd base, pitcher Lucas Luetge to first baseman Logan Morrison to second baseman Robinson Cano.
Brian Dozier lines out to left fielder Rickie Weeks.
Kurt Suzuki grounds out, pitcher Lucas Luetge to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Eduardo Nunez flies out to right fielder Justin Ruggiano.
Joe Mauer grounds into a force out, shortstop Brad Miller to second baseman Robinson Cano.   Torii Hunter out at 2nd.
